- added first-steps.cpp and the first-steps folder, which contains some images to visualize the progress.
This prothgramme shows basic operations with openCV matrix, such as rotation and color inversion.

- added grads_and_etc.cpp and the Gradients folder, which contains some images to visualize the progress.
This programme shows basic operation with gradients by X and Y axes.

- added detectors.cpp and the Detected_dotes folder, which contains some images to visualize the progress.
This programme shows some operations with detectors, descriptors and image matching. There are used different commands for same operations to show the difference between them.

- added base_search.cpp.
This programme saves pictures in the specified folder to a file. There is used a custom "image" structure. 

struct image {
    cv::Mat source;
    std::vector<cv::KeyPoint> keys;
};

  
